      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "它让同一个字母，每次都变成不同的模样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "三百年里无人能解，它就是维吉尼亚密码。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "shift",
      "line_id": "shift-1",
      "filename": "shift-shift-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/shift-shift-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "把每个字母看作零到二十五的编号，加密就是做加法再对二十六取余。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "shift",
      "line_id": "shift-2",
      "filename": "shift-shift-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/shift-shift-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "关键在于，每个位置移动多少，由密钥字母决定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "shift",
      "line_id": "shift-3",
      "filename": "shift-shift-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/shift-shift-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "密钥不够长就循环使用，铺满整段明文。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "tabula",
      "line_id": "tab-1",
      "filename": "tabula-tab-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/tabula-tab-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.71,
      "size": 27360,
      "text": "这张二十六乘二十六的方阵，就是加密的查找表。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "tabula",
      "line_id": "tab-2",
      "filename": "tabula-tab-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/tabula-tab-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "用明文字母选一行，用密钥字母选一列，交点就是密文。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "tabula",
      "line_id": "tab-3",
      "filename": "tabula-tab-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/tabula-tab-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "解密时反过来，沿密钥那一列找回明文所在的行。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "stronger",
      "line_id": "str-1",
      "filename": "stronger-str-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/stronger-str-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.69,
      "size": 43056,
      "text": "凯撒密码只用一个固定偏移，字母频率原样保留，很容易被统计破解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "stronger",
      "line_id": "str-2",
      "filename": "stronger-str-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/stronger-str-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "维吉尼亚用多个移位表交替，把频率抹平，统计分析就失灵了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "输入你的明文和密钥，逐个字母观察它如何被移位。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "看方阵里高亮的行列交点，正是当前这个字母的密文。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "维吉尼亚密码用循环密钥驱动多张移位表，逐字母加密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "它抹平了字母频率，因此远比单表的凯撒密码坚固。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "vigenere-cipher",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/vigenere-cipher/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "一张小小的方阵，藏着三百年的秘密，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
